trans-unit.source: Represents an association set in the conceptual model.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma associação definida no modelo conceitual.

trans-unit.source: In CSDL, an AssociationSet contains the instances of the <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType>.
trans-unit.target: No CSDL, um AssociationSet contém as instâncias de <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType>.</xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType>
Para obter mais informações, consulte [conjuntos de associação (EDM)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a1d39938-e52c-4293-b676-87ee6afe52e5).

trans-unit.source: A collection of type <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection%601> that contains the ends of this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Uma coleção de tipo <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection%601> que contém as extremidades deste <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the built-in type kind for this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o tipo do tipo interno para este <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind"></xref> object that represents built-in type kind for this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind"> </xref> objeto que representa o tipo interno para este <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the association related to this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a associação relacionada a isso <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType"></xref> object that represents the association related to this <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType"> </xref> objeto que representa a associação relacionados a este <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationSet"> </xref>.
